
;introduction:
;
;@FS X    - friendly starbase
;@FP X    - friendly planet
;@ES X    - enemy starbase
;@EP X    - enemy planet
;@NS X    - neutral planet
;
;?T X     - if flag true
;?F X     - if flag false
;
;*T X     - if true, and toggle
;*F X     - if false, and toggle


;starbase 1 stuff...
;
@FS 1     ; at friendly starbase 1...

*F1       ; flag 1 false?

"Please go to @FP 1."

?T2       ; flag 2 true?

"Congratulations!"

?F2       ; else...

"Wrong!"


;friendly planet 1 stuff...
;
@FP 1     ; at friendly planet 1...

*F3       ; first time message

"Please return to starbase."

*T3       ;second message

"You've already been here, fool."



